---
import BaseLayout from "../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
---

<BaseLayout
  title="关于 Asa Zhou"
  description="认识 Asa Zhou：开发者、写作者与数字花园的长期维护者。"
  path="/about/"
  page="about"
>
  <main id="main-content" class="about-page">
    <header class="about-hero">
      <div class="about-hero__meta" data-hero-fade>
        <span>INDEX / 02</span>
        <span>HUMAN PROFILE</span>
        <span>OPEN FILE</span>
      </div>
      <div class="about-hero__title" aria-label="About Asa Zhou">
        <span class="title-clip"><span data-hero-line>ABOUT</span></span>
        <span class="title-clip title-clip--right"><span data-hero-line>ASA</span></span>
      </div>
      <div class="about-hero__portrait" aria-hidden="true" data-parallax="-7">
        <span></span><span></span><span></span>
        <strong>AZ</strong>
      </div>
      <p class="about-hero__intro" data-hero-fade>
        我是 Asa，一名喜欢<span>把模糊变清晰</span>的开发者与创作者。
        我用代码搭建体验，用文字保存判断，也用长期项目检验想法。
      </p>
    </header>

    <section class="about-profile" aria-labelledby="profile-title">
      <div class="section-marker" data-reveal>
        <span>01</span>
        <p>Profile<br />自我介绍</p>
      </div>
      <div class="about-profile__grid">
        <h1 id="profile-title" data-reveal>Make it clear.<br /><em>Make it last.</em></h1>
        <div data-reveal>
          <p>
            我关注前端工程、界面设计、内容系统与独立创作。比起只把功能做出来，
            我更在意一件作品如何被理解、如何被使用，以及它能不能在时间里继续生长。
          </p>
          <p>
            这个博客是我的公开工作台。完整文章负责说明结论，过程笔记负责保留现场，
            项目记录则负责展示一个想法如何经受真实世界的摩擦。
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="about-now" aria-labelledby="now-title">
      <div class="about-now__dial" data-reveal aria-hidden="true">
        <span class="dial-ring dial-ring--outer"></span>
        <span class="dial-ring dial-ring--inner"></span>
        <span class="dial-hand"></span>
        <strong>NOW</strong>
        <small>MMXXVI</small>
      </div>
      <div class="about-now__copy" data-reveal>
        <p>NOW / 当前坐标</p>
        <h2 id="now-title">正在把知识、工具和审美，装进同一个长期系统。</h2>
        <ul>
          <li><span>01</span><div><strong>Building</strong><p>设计并维护这座可以持续发布、检索与连接内容的数字花园。</p></div></li>
          <li><span>02</span><div><strong>Learning</strong><p>继续研究浏览器图形、动效叙事和更高效的独立创作工作流。</p></div></li>
          <li><span>03</span><div><strong>Writing</strong><p>记录真实项目里的决策、失败、修正，以及最后真正有效的方法。</p></div></li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="toolbox" aria-labelledby="toolbox-title">
      <header data-reveal>
        <span>02 / TOOLBOX</span>
        <h2 id="toolbox-title">工具会变化，<br />判断力会留下。</h2>
      </header>
      <div class="toolbox__grid">
        <article data-reveal>
          <span>BUILD</span>
          <h3>Web Engineering</h3>
          <p>TypeScript · Astro · React · Node.js · WebGL · Performance</p>
        </article>
        <article data-reveal>
          <span>SHAPE</span>
          <h3>Interface Design</h3>
          <p>Design Systems · Interaction · Prototyping · Motion · Accessibility</p>
        </article>
        <article data-reveal>
          <span>THINK</span>
          <h3>Content & Product</h3>
          <p>Information Architecture · UX Writing · Product Thinking · Documentation</p>
        </article>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="about-contact" data-reveal>
      <p>如果你也在构建值得长期存在的东西，欢迎来交换想法。</p>
      <h2>Let’s make<br /><em>something last.</em></h2>
      <a href="https://github.com/AsaZhou923" data-cursor="HELLO">
        <span>从 GitHub 找到我</span>
        <svg viewBox="0 0 64 64" aria-hidden="true"><circle cx="32" cy="32" r="29" /><path d="M19 32h26M36 23l9 9-9 9" /></svg>
      </a>
    </section>
  </main>
</BaseLayout>
